<br>
For openers, just sit back and compare his speech to some of the rants we have seen recently coming from the likes of Howard Dean. There is no comparison. We have a thoughtful, principled, caring, polished, and courageous President which is in stark comparison to a loud-mouthed, obnoxious, wanna-be.<br>
<br>
I truly beleive that come time to vote in Nov, that the majority of Americans will choose GWB. The Dems will see their party get the lowest vote count in 30 years. Even lower than Ronald Reagans second term election. My reason for this prediction is rather simple... The Dems, being run by the far left, have lost touch with the average American citizen. They treat the common man &amp; woman as imbiciles, incapable of getting through each day unless the Dems guide them each step of the way. I have news for the Dems, the American people are sick of it! The average American, which I proudly call myself, are NOT stupid, and do NOT need the Dems telling them how to think, act, live, pray, spend, work or vote! This is going to help destroy the Democratic party, or what I have tagged as TDAD &quot;The Dems Are Dying&quot;. With a sigh of relief I say... Good riddance!<br>
